OL,3,CKing's Christmas message to reflect on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,FIn a break with recent tradition, King
OL,7,FCharles has chosen to record this
OL,8,Fyear's Christmas message in a tiny
OL,9,Fhospital chapel, to reflect on the
OL,10,Fchallenging year both he and his
OL,11,Fdaughter-in-law, Kate, have
OL,12,Fexperienced battling cancer.
OL,14,FThe King asked to move the broadcast
OL,15,Flocation away from a royal residence
OL,16,Fand tasked the production team with
OL,17,Ffinding a place that had a health
OL,18,Fconnection but was still a spiritual
OL,19,Fand community space.
