OL,3,CKing's Christmas message to reflect on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,FThe venue was the Fitzrovia Chapel,
OL,7,Fonce a place of worship and
OL,8,Fcontemplation for patients and medical
OL,9,Fstaff of the Middlesex hospital which
OL,10,Fsurrounded it.
OL,12,FThe hospital, which was merged with
OL,13,FUniversity College Hospital London,
OL,14,Fwas demolished but the tiny 18th
OL,15,FCentury chapel was left untouched as
OL,16,Fthe site was redeveloped.
