OL,3,CKing's Christmas message to reflect on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,FIt's the first time since 2006 that a
OL,7,Fmonarch has chosen to record the
OL,8,Ftraditional speech away from a
OL,9,Fresidence like Buckingham Palace or
OL,10,FWindsor Castle.
OL,12,FThe King wanted this year's message to
OL,13,Freflect on the challenging year he has
OL,14,Fsuffered following his cancer
OL,15,Fdiagnosis for which he is still
OL,16,Freceiving treatment.
