OL,3,CKing's Christmas message to reflect on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,FThe location also means the King has
OL,7,Fincluded the Princess of Wales in his
OL,8,Fthoughts after she had her own cancer
OL,9,Fdiagnosis followed by a course of
OL,10,Fchemotherapy.
OL,12,FThe year-end speech, always broadcast
OL,13,Fat 3pm on Christmas Day, is Charles'
OL,14,Fthird since he ascended to the throne.
OL,16,FHis previous speeches were recorded at
OL,17,FSt George's Chapel inside Windsor
OL,18,FCastle and in the Centre Room at
OL,19,FBuckingham Palace overlooking The Mall.
