OL,6,FFitzrovia Chapel is just moments away
OL,7,Ffrom London's busy Oxford Street shops
OL,8,Fbut provides a quiet, secluded and
OL,9,Fpeaceful place for all faiths.
OL,11,FIt retains a link to the newly-built
OL,12,FUCLH hospital in nearby Euston.
OL,14,FThe Grade II* listed building has a
OL,15,Fplain exterior but inside, it is
OL,16,Fdecorated in a Gothic revival style
OL,17,Fwith marble and gold leaf and
OL,18,FByzantine-inspired architecture.
