OL,11,FThe King agreed on the location
OL,12,Fwithout visiting the chapel.
OL,14,F"He was pretty surprised and kind of
OL,15,Fdelighted, as far as I can tell, from
OL,16,Fcoming in and discovering it", said
OL,17,FCarla Whalen, chair of the Fitzrovia
OL,18,FChapel Foundation's board of trustees.
