OL,6,FA royal source described the King as
OL,7,Fbeing "bowled over" by its beauty and
OL,8,Fthe fact that its location is largely
OL,9,Funknown.
OL,11,FMs Whalen added: "He was very
OL,12,Finterested in the marble, there's 40
OL,13,Ftypes of marble here and lots of
OL,14,Fdifferent designs and he wanted to
OL,15,Flearn about the history of the chapel
OL,16,Fand some of the people who are
OL,17,Fcommemorated here.
